      <p>Value iteration can be used in conjunction with action-value function, which takes the following update:
\begin{align}
q_{k+1}(s,a)&amp;\doteq\mathbb{E}\left[R_{t+1}+\gamma\max_{a‚Äô}q_k(S_{t+1},a‚Äô)|S_t=s,A_t=a\right] \\ &amp;=\sum_{s‚Äô,r}p(s‚Äô,r|s,a)\left[r+\gamma\max_{a‚Äô}q_k(s‚Äô,a‚Äô)\right]
\end{align}
